reviews.text: As here is CEO version Neway, it is grander and with better and faster customer services, also no "bad guys" or "gangsters" or whatever you want to call them are around so it's safe to hang around *\(^o^)/*
Good price and ok food. Too few Mandarin songs.

It was quite fun to sing there, food and Karoke for under 100 dollars, but near the end with 15 minutes left they had an error and the machine stopped working for all rooms so we had a long wait and called the staff but we got cut off, later we talked to the staff and told us everyone had the same problem, then after 30 minutes a staff came in and said "yours still isn't fixed" and we were quite shocked as they hadn't told us that it had been fixed. But we were compensated with 1 hour, overall it was fun, and I would come again, but the error and  staff not telling us that the error was over was quite fustrating, so overall I rate that a 3/5

Large variety of rooms that can fit up to 50 people. Not especially great for American pop songs and some songs didn't display the lyrics... which is the point of karaoke... the buffet offered a hot pot option so that won back some points.
Sound system is getting worse.  Backdround noise problem is serious.

result.name: 宜家家居餐廳

reviews.text: 除咗有啲嘢整定， 耐咗 ，冇咁好食之外 ， 其他食品都令人十分滿意， 略加少少費用就可以加倍滿足到你嘅食慾！服務有禮 極好嘅選擇！
可自選配搭各款食物，味道不錯而且價錢合理，咖啡可添飲，還有沙拉、湯麵、糯米雞等美食
食物質素其實一般，還可以，人流不多時，環境舒適，我就幾喜歡，但有時人流太多，就不好了。
價錢大眾化，自助式，免費添飲咖啡茶水，唯獨有部分顧客，自私及貪心，不付費飲咖啡茶汽水！
我常在這裏買家庭厨房用品，很實用，價錢合理，我孫女們和我還可以吃我們喜歡的瑞典肉丸餐，我們許多時去宜家家居吃完餐後再逛傢俬一天遊。
